    "body": "We currently default to 20 threads for the multi threaded shuffle [writer](https://github.com/NVIDIA/spark-rapids/blob/branch-22.12/sql-plugin/src/main/scala/com/nvidia/spark/rapids/RapidsConf.scala#L1338) and [reader](https://github.com/NVIDIA/spark-rapids/blob/branch-22.12/sql-plugin/src/main/scala/com/nvidia/spark/rapids/RapidsConf.scala#L1348) pools. \r\n\r\nThe plugin should be smarter about this configuration, not unlike what was done with the [multi threaded file reader](https://github.com/NVIDIA/spark-rapids/blob/branch-22.12/sql-plugin/src/main/scala/com/nvidia/spark/rapids/RapidsConf.scala#L729).",
